en_153489_0	Former Chairman of the SLTB Shashi Welgama and another individual were further remanded today, as per the order from the Colombo Additional Magistrate Aruna Buddhadasa.
en_153489_1	Both suspects have been accused of the misuse of 125 million rupees, in the purchase of a spare parts deal for the SLTB.
en_153489_2	When the Case was taken for hearing this morning, the CID informed the Court that investigations are being carried out, to arrest the 3rd suspect in the incident.
en_153489_3	CID also told Courts that the 3rd suspect who was a former financial manager of the SLTB has already fled the country.
